<bibRefCitation author="Topsent, E." box="[381,553,824,850]" pageId="5" pageNumber="142" pagination="1 - 280" refId="ref7517" refString="Topsent, E. (1904) Spongiaires des Acores. Resultats des campagnes scientifiques accomplies par le Prince Albert I. Monaco, 25, 1 - 280, pls. 1 - 18. https: // doi. org / 10.5962 / bhl. title. 61852" type="journal article" year="1904">Topsent, 1904</bibRefCitation>
